channel.title: Very important news
channel.description:
Japanese scientist placed an explosive detonator in the bottom of Lake Locnas to blow Nessi out of the water. Sequor Godfree of the Nessi alliance summoned the help of Scotland's local wizards to cast a protective spell upon the lake and its local residents and all those who seek the continual peaceful existence of our underwater ally.
Save Nessi please magical wizards!! :(
(if you dont get it, you need to watch napoleon dynamite)
